				</div>
				
			
            <h3 class="red-border-bottom">Overview</h3>
            <!-- FOCUS HEADING -->

			<p>BKP Technologies, Inc., based in Newton, MA, is a professional services and software development company that delivers innovative Information Technology (IT) services and products for the life sciences and healthcare industries.</p>	

        </div>

        
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-3 focus-box" data-scrollreveal="enter left after 0.15s over 1s">

						
				<div class="service-icon">
					
										
						<a href="/our-services"><i class="pixeden" style="background:url(http://www.bkptech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/expertise_logo_small.jpg) no-repeat center;width:100%; height:100%;"></i> <!-- FOCUS ICON--></a>
					
					
				</div>
				
			
            <h3 class="red-border-bottom">Expertise</h3>
            <!-- FOCUS HEADING -->

			<p>Our areas of expertise include, Product Safety and Pharmacovigilance (PV) Systems,  Adverse Event and Drug Coding Systems, PV Signaling and Data Mining Solutions, Web/Intranet and Mobile Application Development, Clinical Data Management and Electronic Data Capture Systems, Systems Validation, and Data Migration.</p>	

        </div>

        
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-3 focus-box" data-scrollreveal="enter left after 0.15s over 1s">

						
				<div class="service-icon">
					
										
						<a href="/bkp-codex-suite/"><i class="pixeden" style="background:url(http://www.bkptech.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/meddra_logo_small.jpg) no-repeat center;width:100%; height:100%;"></i> <!-- FOCUS ICON--></a>
					
					
				</div>
				
			
            <h3 class="red-border-bottom">MedDRA Tools</h3>
            <!-- FOCUS HEADING -->

			<p>The <strong>BKP Codex Suite</strong> of tools includes <strong>BKP Codex</strong>, a powerful MedDRA/ WHODRL coding tool and <strong>BKP Codex: Up-Version</strong> a robust tool for up-versioning MedDRA coded terms in Oracle Argus Safety™.</p>	

        </div>

