		<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 column zerif-rtl-big-title"><div class="big-intro" data-scrollreveal="enter left after 0s over 1s">Innovative and Cost Effective Technology Solutions</div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 column zerif_about_us_center text_and_skills" data-scrollreveal="enter bottom after 0s over 1s"><p>BKP Technologies, Inc. provides specialized technology solutions and services to the pharmaceutical, biotech and medical device industries.  BKP currently serves many clients throughout the world in these highly regulated environments.  BKP Technologies specializes in the areas of Systems Design and Implementation, Web Application/Database Design and Development, and Systems Validation. Our staff of highly experienced consultants create and develop innovative and cost effective technologies which support the needs of our client base.<br /><br />Focusing on these regulated industries has allowed us to develop an extensive understanding of the changing needs of scientific companies throughout the development lifecycle and the needs of companies who market products and services to the scientific sector.  BKP Technologies is committed to supplementing our customers' in-house staff by providing mission-critical services which augment our customers' core competencies. </p></div>		<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 column zerif-rtl-skills ">

